story: MIT African Students' Association - ASA added an event.
message:
First General body meeting of the year. Come, let's set the bar high, and plan for the future of the community!!!

Join the community for a night of GAMES, MUSIC, FOOD, and FUN. 
Variety of games, including traditional African games, so you will be sure to find a new game you enjoy.

And did I mention FOOD?!?!?!
